53:30.344 --> 53:38.654
♪ ♪

53:38.753 --> 53:47.184
♪ ♪

53:47.186 --> 53:49.796
[DOOR OPENS]

53:49.798 --> 53:51.145
[BEEPING, HISSING CONTINUE]

53:51.147 --> 53:53.060
[DOOR CLOSES]

53:53.062 --> 53:58.761
♪ ♪

53:58.831 --> 54:07.331
♪ ♪

54:07.432 --> 54:12.297
♪ ♪

54:12.299 --> 54:13.994
[STAIRS CREAKING]

54:13.996 --> 54:16.083
♪ ♪

54:16.085 --> 54:18.694
[PANTING]

54:18.696 --> 54:24.128
♪ ♪

54:24.131 --> 54:29.313
BRADY: History is a graveyard
for unsustainable frontiers.

54:29.316 --> 54:32.447
The world was flat...

54:32.449 --> 54:34.406
until it wasn't.

54:34.408 --> 54:37.060
[GROANS]

54:37.062 --> 54:40.412
Gods lived on Mount Olympus...

54:40.414 --> 54:43.415
until they didn't.

54:43.417 --> 54:48.463
Polio, mumps, measles,
malaria... all incurable...

54:48.465 --> 54:49.986
until they weren't.

54:49.988 --> 54:53.120
♪ ♪

54:53.122 --> 54:57.559
We sent a monkey into space...

54:57.561 --> 54:59.779
and then a man...

54:59.781 --> 55:03.173
and then space stations and satellites.

55:03.175 --> 55:05.088
[GROANS]

55:05.160 --> 55:15.447
♪ ♪

55:15.557 --> 55:24.194
♪ ♪

55:24.196 --> 55:26.414
We crossed oceans...

55:26.416 --> 55:27.674
[MOANS]

55:27.677 --> 55:31.113
...discovered new
worlds, and stole them.

55:31.116 --> 55:32.725
[GROANS]

55:32.727 --> 55:34.204
[GASPING]

55:34.206 --> 55:40.472
♪ ♪

55:40.557 --> 55:48.305
♪ ♪

55:48.307 --> 55:51.091
We encroach. We infiltrate.

55:51.093 --> 55:55.791
We slaughter. We rape. We dominate.

55:55.793 --> 55:57.227
Why?

55:57.229 --> 55:59.404
Simple...

55:59.406 --> 56:01.971
We refuse to accept death.

56:01.973 --> 56:04.539
[LAUGHING]

56:04.541 --> 56:12.112
♪ ♪

56:12.198 --> 56:21.948
♪ ♪

56:22.037 --> 56:29.956
♪ ♪

56:29.958 --> 56:32.437
So every act of conquest

56:32.439 --> 56:36.291
is a step toward acquiring
fresher and fresher knowledge

56:36.294 --> 56:37.859
of the ultimate frontier.

56:37.862 --> 56:39.618
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

56:39.620 --> 56:47.354
♪ ♪

56:47.456 --> 56:55.198
♪ ♪

56:55.287 --> 57:03.163
♪ ♪

57:03.253 --> 57:10.901
♪ ♪

57:10.904 --> 57:12.384
[WEAKLY] Chaos...

57:15.394 --> 57:17.177
Chaos.

57:17.179 --> 57:21.050
Because the collective, atavistic,

57:21.052 --> 57:23.836
evolutionary ambition of humanity is,

57:23.838 --> 57:27.840
and always has been, immortality.

57:27.842 --> 57:30.277
Chaos.

57:30.279 --> 57:32.018
[KNOCKING ON GLASS]

57:32.020 --> 57:33.500
Chaos.

57:34.682 --> 57:36.936
[ECHOING] Chaos!

